    narr:narration """This hub tracks the interplay between typographic rigor and authorial voice. The architecture of the text relies on [ALL-CAPS for architectural finality](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis) and [emphatic assertion](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsIS) to signal non-negotiable design constraints, such as [WHOLE, TOWARD, AWAY](narr:StyleObs_AICompanyizedEmphasis). This high-conviction register is balanced by [bold markdown as terminology control](narr:StyleObs_BoldKeyTerms), which anchors the document's taxonomy through [bold bullet lead-ins](narr:StyleObs_BoldBulletLeadins) and [bolded noun-phrase editorial headers](narr:StyleObs_BoldedSectionHeaders). A singular [bold core insight](narr:StyleObs_BoldCoreInsight) serves as the thesis anchor. Tension arises from the juxtaposition of this authoritative, structural typography with [informal lowercase vernacular](narr:StyleObs_LowercaseProperName) in founder blockquotes. Recent observations highlight a shift toward using [antithetical definition](narr:StyleObs_8) and [clinical analogies](narr:StyleObs_2) (e.g., the eye chart) to ground abstract review concepts, moving beyond simple emphasis into diagnostic, second-person decision heuristics.""" ;
